<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 4" captionStartId="F4" captionText="Figure 4. Leucotrichia chiriquiensis Flint, 1970. Male genitalia: A segments VII-VIII and segment IX margin, lateral B segments IX-X, lateral (base of phallus crosshatched) C segments IX-X, dorsal D segments VII-IX, ventral E phallus, lateral F phallus, dorsal. Modified from Thomson and Holzenthal (2015)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1111.77371.figure4" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/713492" pageId="0" pageNumber="425">, 4</figureCitation>
